page.title: 05DARTMOOR FIRING RANGES
page.content: Red flags flying on hills denotes that firing is taking place, but do not mark the limit of the range boundary. The boundary is marked by noticed boards and red and white posts. When red flags are flying DO NOT CROSS the range boundary. Do not touch any object on the moor - it may be dangerous.
